data.description: 2-1 buy down with accepted offer and price refresh, just in time for the holidays. Sitting on top of a full basement, prepare to be captivated by the open-concept layout that creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones. The kitchen is a culinary dream come true, boasting modern stainless-steel appliances that effortlessly blend form and function. Whether you're preparing a gourmet feast or whipping up a quick meal, this well-appointed kitchen will inspire your inner chef. Escape to the tranquility of your own private oasis in the generously sized backyard. With its fully fenced and leveled design, this outdoor space provides the ideal setting for hosting memorable gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day. Let the soothing sounds of nature and the gentle breeze create the perfect ambiance as you relax and recharge. The primary suite is an expansive retreat within your own home. Immerse yourself in luxury as you discover a spacious en-suite bathroom complete with his and her closets. For those chilly evenings, cozy up by the fireplace and indulge in a moment of quiet relaxation. This residence combines impeccable style with convenience. Enjoy easy access to nearby amenities such as shopping centers, restaurants, and recreational facilities. With its prime location, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. This property is not just a house; it's a sanctuary where cherished memories will be made. Whether you're looking to host grand gatherings or seeking a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life, this home has it all. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the true essence of luxury living in a home that offers both elegance and comfort.
